These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, drama, satire, zombie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, cricket, baseball
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, roller, train, scooter
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
 2. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##8
 5. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 8. the person watching zombie movies is between the person driving the roller and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 9. the person driving the scooter is the person watching satire movies##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
13. the person watching satire movies is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person driving the train##1
15. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | card-games     | sudoku   | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie   | horror   | satire  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket  | baseball  | badminton |
| Transport     | ship    | train | roller     | scooter    |

