.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, cola, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, mango, garlic, avocado
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, ambient, dubstep, techno
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rat, goat, bird
 1. the fan of dubstep is between the owner of the turtle and the fan of ambient##2
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
 4. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
 5. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
 6. the person eating avocado is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
 8. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of disco is the owner of the rat##1
10. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
11. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
12. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
13. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
14. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
15. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
17. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
18. the person eating mango is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
19. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | juice | cola | almond-milk  | tea  |
| Food          | avocado     | mango | raspberry | garlic  |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | dubstep  | techno | disco |
| Pet           | goat | bird | turtle    | rat  |

