.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing, chess, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, scientific, comedy, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, salsa, indie, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, badminton, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8
 7. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
11. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking    | traveling   | chess | fishing |
