.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, papaya, avocado, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, baking, drawing, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, journalist, mechanic, architect
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, cricket, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the fisherman##6
 2. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 3. the person eating raspberry is the mechanic##1
 4. the person eating papaya is between the fisherman and the journalist##2
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person eating papaya##8
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the architect##1
10. the journalist is the person who's sport is sailing##1
11. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
12. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
14. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
15. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | avocado    | papaya             | spinach   | raspberry     |
| Hobby   | hiking | drawing            | photography | baking    |
| Job     | journalist | architect | fisherman  | mechanic |
| Sport   | sailing  | cricket               | soccer  | volleyball   |

