 4. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 5. the person driving the car is the mexican##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the brazilian##8
 7. the person drinking coffee is not the russian##6
 8. the coach is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person drinking coffee##7
 9. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
10. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the coach##3
11. the paramedic is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the coach is not the indian##6
13. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
14. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the coach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
