10. the writer is not to the left of the writer##8
11. the dancer is on the far left##1
12. the architect is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
14. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
15. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
16. the writer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8

