 3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the fan of salsa##8
11. the fan of house is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
12. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite   | juice     | almond-milk    | cola |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | trance      | house     | salsa     |
| Sport         | sailing | baseball  | skateboarding     | basketball  |
| Transport     | skateboard     | motorbike | roller | tram     |

