The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, punk, blues
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the left of the writer##8
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 4. the pilot is the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the librarian##6
 6. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the fan of electronic##8
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the librarian##8
 8. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
 9. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
10. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
11. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the librarian and the person who's hobby is photography##2
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3

